    <item>
      <title>随着富裕人群涌入棕榈岛，迪拜豪宅销量飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/dubai-mansion-sales-soar-as-wealthy-flock-to-palm-shaped-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管该地区地缘政治紧张局势日益加剧，但全球超级富豪继续涌向中东商业和旅游中心，第一季度迪拜标价 1000 万美元或以上的房屋销量增长了 19%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/dubai-mansion-sales-soar-as-wealthy-flock-to-palm-shaped-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:17:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道富银行坚持逆向押注美联储将在六月降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/state-street-stands-by-contrarian-bet-fed-will-cut-rates-in-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管一系列热门经济数据促使大多数交易者将押注推迟到今年晚些时候，但道富环球投资顾问公司仍然支持美联储最早在 6 月份降息的逆向呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/state-street-stands-by-contrarian-bet-fed-will-cut-rates-in-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
