    <item>
      <title>尽管受到黑客攻击，联合健康集团的利润仍超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/unitedhealth-beats-profit-estimates-despite-hack-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合健康集团 (UnitedHealth Group Inc.) 公布的第一季度利润超出了华尔街的预期，并确认了今年的前景，尽管其子公司遭受的网络攻击给医疗保健行业带来了巨大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/unitedhealth-beats-profit-estimates-despite-hack-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着俄罗斯石油流量增加，印度试图出售美国石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/india-s-reliance-tries-to-sell-us-oil-as-russian-flows-pick-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[信实工业有限公司(Reliance Industries Ltd.)上周向亚洲其他买家提供了美国石油，这对于炼油商来说是一个不寻常的举动，因为他们很少在购买原油后几周内寻求转售原油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/india-s-reliance-tries-to-sell-us-oil-as-russian-flows-pick-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 08:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stellantis 首席执行官 3900 万美元的薪酬因裁员而引起投资者愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stellantis-ceo-s-39-million-pay-package-is-criticized-by-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Stellantis NV 首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯 (Carlos Tavares) 在 2023 年的薪酬上涨受到了阻力，因为这家吉普车制造商在电动汽车转型中追求大幅裁员和严格的节约目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stellantis-ceo-s-39-million-pay-package-is-criticized-by-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 07:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
